-- Brasil Foods and GP Plan to Merge Dairy Units, Exame Says
-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 2012-02-02T16:34:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-02/brasil-foods-and-gp-plan-to-merge-dairy-units-exame-says.html
BRF - Brasil Foods SA  and  GP
Investments Ltd. (GPIV11)  plan to merge dairy units,  Exame  magazine
reported on its website, without saying where it got the
information.  The merged company would have the capacity to process 4
billion liters (1.05 billion gallons) of milk a year, Sao Paulo-
based Exame said.  Brasil Foods  denied merger talks in an e-mailed response to
Bloomberg News. GP Investments declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in Sao Paulo at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  